6187 {
6188  /* vApplicationMallocFailedHook(void) will only be called if
6189  configUSE_MALLOC_FAILED_HOOK is set to 1 in FreeRTOSConfig.h. It is a hook
6190  function that will get called if a call to pvPortMalloc(void) fails.
6191  pvPortMalloc(void) is called internally by the kernel whenever a task, queue,
6192  timer or semaphore is created. It is also called by various parts of the
6193  demo application. If heap_1.c or heap_2.c are used, then the size of the
6194  heap available to pvPortMalloc(void) is defined by configTOTAL_HEAP_SIZE in
6195  FreeRTOSConfig.h, and the xPortGetFreeHeapSize(void) API function can be used
6196  to query the size of free heap space that remains (although it does not
6197  provide information on how the remaining heap might be fragmented). */
6198 #ifndef __L_DEBUG
6199  vReset();
6200 #else
6201 
6202  taskDISABLE_INTERRUPTS();

1349  case SCREENOVERPAY:
1350  case SCREENAUDITREFILLING:
1351  case SCREENVENDUSB:
1352  {
1353  vDisplayLCD("%c - ", eAudit == PERMANENT ? 'P' : 'T');
1354  switch(wEcran)
1355  {
1356  case SCREENVENDCASH:
1357  {
1358  byIndex = CASHTEXT;
1359  break;
1360  }
1361  case SCREENVENDCASHLESS:
1362  {
1363  byIndex = CASHLESSTEXT;
1364  break;
1365  }
1366  case SCREENREVALUECAHSLESS:
1367  {
1368  byIndex = REVALUECASHLESSTEXT;
1369  break;
1370  }
1371  case SCREENOVERPAY:
1372  {
1373  byIndex = OVERPAYTEXTE;
1374  break;
1375  }
1376  case SCREENAUDITREFILLING:
1377  {
1378  byIndex = FILLING;
1379  break;
1380  }
1381  case SCREENVENDUSB:
1382  {
1383  byIndex = VENDUSBTEXT;
1384  break;
1385  }
1386  default:
1387  {
1388  break;
1389  }
1390  }
1391  vDisplayLCD("%s: %.*f\7", byTexte[byIndex], byDecimalPos, (double)(*(DWORD*)vParameter) / wCurrencyDivider);
1392  LCDGotoXY(1, 2);
1393  vDisplayLCD("(*)%-17s(#)%-17s", byTexte[BACK], byTexte[NEXT]);
1394  break;
1395  }
1396  case SCREENMACHINES:
1397  case SCREENINCG:
1398  case SCREENOUTCG:
1399  case SCREENINBV:
1400  {
1401  if((byIndexSelectedMachine > MAXMACHINES) && (wEcran == SCREENMACHINES))
1402  {
1403  wEcran = SCREENAUDITREFILLING;
1404  byIndexSelectedMachine = 0;
1405  xQueueSendToBack(queueKeyHit, &byIndex, 0);
1406  }
1407  else
1408  {
1409  vDisplayLCD("%c - ", eAudit == PERMANENT ? 'P' : 'T');
1410  switch(wEcran)
1411  {
1412  case SCREENMACHINES:
1413  {
1414  while((byIndexSelectedMachine < MAXMACHINES) && (modules[byIndexSelectedMachine].config.byNumero > 100))
1415  {
1416  byIndexSelectedMachine++;
1417  }
1418  if(byIndexSelectedMachine < MAXMACHINES)
1419  {
1420  vDisplayLCD("%s %u: %u", byTexte[SERVICE], modules[byIndexSelectedMachine].config.byNumero,
1421  (eAudit == TEMPORARY) ? auditData.data.wNumberServices[byIndexSelectedMachine] :
1422  auditDataPermanent.data.wNumberServices[byIndexSelectedMachine]);
1423  }
1424  break;
1425  }
1426  case SCREENINCG:
1427  case SCREENOUTCG:
1428  {
1429  while((byCashPos < MAXNUMBERCHANNELSCG) && ((changeGiverConfig.byCoinValue[byCashPos] == 0XFF) ||
1430  (changeGiverConfig.byCoinValue[byCashPos] == 0X00)))
1431  {
1432  byCashPos++;
1433  }
1434  if(byCashPos < MAXNUMBERCHANNELSCG)
1435  {
1436  if(wEcran == SCREENINCG)
1437  {
1438  vDisplayLCD(byTexte[COININ], byDecimalPos,
1439  (double)(changeGiverConfig.byCoinValue[byCashPos] * changeGiverConfig.deviceConfig.byScaleFactor) /
1440  wCurrencyDivider, (eAudit == TEMPORARY) ? auditData.data.wNumberChannelCGIn[byCashPos] :
1441  auditDataPermanent.data.wNumberChannelCGIn[byCashPos]);
1442  }
1443  else
1444  {
1445  vDisplayLCD(byTexte[COINOUT], byDecimalPos,
1446  (double)(changeGiverConfig.byCoinValue[byCashPos] * changeGiverConfig.deviceConfig.byScaleFactor) /
1447  wCurrencyDivider, (eAudit == TEMPORARY) ? auditData.data.wNumberChannelCGOut[byCashPos] :
1448  auditDataPermanent.data.wNumberChannelCGOut[byCashPos]);
1449  }
1450  }
1451  break;
1452  }
1453  case SCREENINBV:
1454  {
1455  while((byCashPos < MAXNUMBERCHANNELSBV) && ((billValidatorSetup.byBillValue[byCashPos] == 0XFF) ||
1456  (billValidatorSetup.byBillValue[byCashPos] == 0X00)))
1457  {
1458  byCashPos++;
1459  }
1460  if(byCashPos < MAXNUMBERCHANNELSBV)
1461  {
1462  vDisplayLCD(byTexte[BILLIN], byDecimalPos,
1463  (double)(billValidatorSetup.byBillValue[byCashPos] * billValidatorSetup.wScaleFactor) /
1464  wCurrencyDivider, (eAudit == TEMPORARY) ? auditData.data.wNumberChannelBV[byCashPos] :
1465  auditDataPermanent.data.wNumberChannelBV[byCashPos]);
1466  }
1467  break;
1468  }
1469  case SCREENCUMUL:
1470  {
1471  vDisplayLCD("%s%8s%c", byTexte[(wEcran == SCREENBILLACCEPTED) ? CUMUL : DSPTIMEREMAINING], byTexte[DISABLE], !*(BYTE*)vParameter ? 127 : 32);
1472  vDisplayLCD("%8s%c", byTexte[ENABLE], *(BYTE*)vParameter ? 127 : 32);
1473  LCDGotoXY(1, 2);
1474  vDisplayLCD("(*)%-17s(#)%-17s", byTexte[BACK], byTexte[NEXT]);
1475  break;
1476  }
1477 
1478  default:
1479  {
1480  break;
1481  }
1482  }
1483  }
1484  if((byCashPos < MAXCASHCHANNELS) && (byIndexSelectedMachine < MAXMACHINES))
1485  {
1486  LCDGotoXY(1, 2);
1487  vDisplayLCD("(*)%-17s(#)%-17s", byTexte[BACK], byTexte[NEXT]);
1488  }
1489  else
1490  {
1491  byCashPos = 0;
1492  byIndexSelectedMachine = 0;
1493  ((!isRAZEnable || (eAudit == PERMANENT)) && (wEcran == SCREENINBV)) ? wEcran = SCREENAUDIT : wEcran++;
1494  byIndex = 0XFF;
1495  xQueueSendToBack(queueKeyHit, &byIndex, 0);
1496  }
1497  break;
1498  }
1499  case SCREENRAZAUDIT:
1500  {
1501  vDisplayLCD("%s %s %s", byTexte[RAZAUDIT], byTexte[NO], byTexte[YES]);
1502  break;
1503  }
1504  case SCREENHISTORIQUE:
1505  {
1506  vDisplayLCD("%s", (BYTE*)vParameter);
1507  LCDGotoXY(1, 2);
1508  vDisplayLCD("(0)%s (1)%s %s", byTexte[BACK], byTexte[NEXT], byTexte[EXIT]);
1509  byIndex = 0XFF; //Empêche le délai pour l'affichage;
1510  break;
1511  }
1512  case SCREENFILLING:
1513  {
1514  xTimerStart(hTimerTOKBD, 1000);
1515  isFillingInProgress = TRUE;
1516  if(*(BYTE*)vParameter == 0XFF)
1517  {
1518  lAmountCG = 0;
1519  isEnableChanger(TRUE, &centralParameters.coinType);
1520  DelayMs(10);
1521  }
1522  vDisplayLCD("%s %.*f\7 %s %.*f\7", byTexte[COIN], byDecimalPos, *(BYTE*)vParameter > 0X0F ? 0 :
1523  (double)(changeGiverConfig.byCoinValue[*(BYTE*)vParameter] * changeGiverConfig.deviceConfig.byScaleFactor) / wCurrencyDivider,
1524  byTexte[TOTAL], byDecimalPos, (double)lAmountCG / wCurrencyDivider);
1525  LCDGotoXY(1, 2);
1526  vDisplayLCD("%s %s", byTexte[INSERTCOIN], byTexte[EXIT]);
1527  break;
1528  }
1529 
1530  }
1531 
1532  LCD_CURSOR_SET(wEcran == SCREENDATETIME ||
1533  wEcran == SCREENPRICECASH ||

4530  taskYIELD();
4531  }

4541  {

4545  xTimerStart(hTimerTOKBD, 10);
4546  byBillNumber = byMDBBVBuffer[byIndex] & 0X0F;
4547  lAmountBV += billValidatorSetup.byBillValue[byBillNumber] *
4548  billValidatorSetup.wScaleFactor;

4565  }
4566  isChangeAutorized = TRUE;
4567  }

4569  }

4574  case JUST_RESET_BV:

4615  // <editor-fold defaultstate="collapsed" desc="Cashless">

4630  }
4631  }
4632  else
4633  {

4647 
4648  break;

4663  {

4665  }
4666  break;
4667  }// </editor-fold>
4668  case RSP_DISPLAY_REQUEST: //02 Demande d'affichage. Non traité par ce software

4672  break;
4673  }// </editor-fold>

4681  lAmountCL = byMDBCLBuffer[1] * 256 + byMDBCLBuffer[2]; //Calcul du montant de la clé sur le support

4683  byMDBCLBuffer[4] * 0x10000 +
4684  byMDBCLBuffer[5] * 0x100 +
4685  byMDBCLBuffer[6]; //Calcul de l'identifiant unique de la clé

4688  break;

3851  {

3867  break;
3868  }
3869  case SCREENAUDITREFILLING:
3870  {

3872  break;
3873  }

3877  break;
3878  }
3879  default:
3880  {
3881  break;
3882  }
3883  }

3930  break;
3931  }

3933  {
3934  break;
3935  }
3936  }
3937  break;
3938  }
3939  case SCREENMACHINES:

3944  {

3946  if(byIndexSelectedMachine >= MAXMACHINES)
3947  {
3948  wEcran--;
3949  dwValue = (eAudit == TEMPORARY) ? auditData.data.dwOverPay : auditDataPermanent.data.dwOverPay;
3950  }
3951  break;
3952  }
3953  case SHARP:
3954  {
3955  byIndexSelectedMachine++;
3956  break;
3957  }
3958  default:

3960  break;
3961  }
3962  }
3963  isReturnMaintenance = TRUE;
3964  break;
3965  }
3966  case SCREENINCG:
3967  case SCREENOUTCG:
3968  case SCREENINBV:
3969  {
3970  switch(byKeyHit)
3971  {
3972  case STAR:
3973  {
3974  if(byCashPos)
3975  {
3976  byCashPos--;
3977  }
3978  else
3979  {
3980  wEcran--;
3981  //Récupère l'index de la dernière machine.
3982  byIndexSelectedMachine = MAXMACHINES;
3983  while((--byIndexSelectedMachine < MAXMACHINES) && modules[byIndexSelectedMachine].config.byNumero > 99);
3984  //Récupère l'index du dernier canal utile du rendeur.
3985  byCashPos = MAXCASHCHANNELS;
3986  while(--byCashPos && ((changeGiverConfig.byCoinValue[byCashPos] == 0XFF) ||
3987  (changeGiverConfig.byCoinValue[byCashPos] == 0x00)));

3990  wEcran--;
3991  dwValue = (eAudit == TEMPORARY) ? auditData.data.dwOverPay : auditDataPermanent.data.dwOverPay;
3992  }
3993  }
3994  break;
3995  }
3996  case SHARP:
3997  {
3998  ((wEcran == SCREENINBV) && (eAudit == PERMANENT) && byCashPos >= MAXNUMBERCHANNELSBV) ?
3999  wEcran = SCREENMAINMAINTENANCE :
4000  byCashPos < MAXCASHCHANNELS ? byCashPos++ : wEcran++;
4001  break;
4002  }
4003  default:
4004  {
4005  break;
4006  }
4007  }
4008  isReturnMaintenance = TRUE;
4009  break;
4010  }
4011  case SCREENRAZAUDIT:
4012  {

4014  {
4015  case SHARP:
4016  {

4018  }
4019  /* fall trough */

4055  break;

4060  }
4061  }
4062  }// </editor-fold>

4066  }
